column5: What's going on with 53 at Duluth by now? Is it done and is there a decent way through or around Duluth? Thanks. VANT
I don't know if it is done, but I think that the detour that they have you use is better than taking 53. You just go N on I-35 to Messabi to MN-194.
The highway work is all done. Very user friendly and nice road. It has been open for a few months now.
GREAT!! Less than 20 days to go.
Thanks guys, it seemed like it took forever to get through Duluth last year. Which of those two routes do you think is faster? VANT
The current route is the fastest.
By current route, do you mean 53 now that it is done? Thanks, VANT
